Version:    1.4.0

Releases:   https://github.com/utatti/perfect-scrollbar/releases

Homepage:   https://github.com/utatti/perfect-scrollbar

Notes:      When updating the perfect-scrollbar version please note the following:
            - Modify the perfect-scrollbar.css
                - Set all background colors (beside transparent): "background-color: #f3f3fa;"
                - Set all radius: "border-radius: 1px;"
                - Set Opacity of rails: "opacity: 0.2;"
                - Remove the background-color for the hover state
            - There is no min.css in the repo, so I have to minify by myself